Vidiun Ruby API Client Library.
Compatible with Vidiun server version @VERSION@ and above.

This source contains:
 - The Vidiun client library (vidiun_client_base.rb)
 - Auto generated core APIs (vidiun_client.rb)
 - Auto generated plugin APIs (vidiun_plugins/*.rb)
 - Ruby library test code and data files (test/*)
 
== DEPENDENCIES ==

RAKE			(http://rake.rubyforge.org/)
Shoulda			(gem install shoulda)
Rest_client		(gem install rest-client)

== RUNNING THE CLIENT LIBRARY TESTS ==

IMPORTANT: never run the tests of the client library against a production account - 
	these tests perform modifications to account profiles.
	
Update vidiun.yml with your account information
Change directory to vidiun/ruby
Execute the command: rake test
